text: MAFF may refer to: * MAFF (gene), a transcription factor * Malmö Arab Film Festival, held in Malmö (Sweden), the largest Arabic film festival in Europe * Ministry of Agriculture, Fisheries and Food (United Kingdom), a former department of UK government * Ministry of Agriculture, Forestry and Fisheries, Cambodia * Ministry of Agriculture, Forestry and Fisheries (Japan) * Mozilla Archive Format, a web page archiving format provided by Firefox through an extension
title: MAFF
